profile_positions.description:
• Full ownership on partnerships website for affiliate and strategic partners. Stack: Drupal + Marketo & Salesforce integration; 
• Customer journey mapping to improve product adoption; 
• Performance marketing campaigns (hands-on: Linkedin, Facebook, Instagram, Outbrain, Terminus, Demandbase) - optimised conversion by 280% with bidding automation and implementing A/B testing; 
• Integrated cross-channel marketing campaigns with an emphasis on digital, social media and EMK;
• Lead generation, demand generation, ABM (Account Based Marketing);
• Creative production and content marketing (video, white papers, customer testimonials, sales enablement, etc.); 
• Marketing automation (Marketo, Salesforce);
• Partner marketing and relationship management with external stakeholders (AMEX GBT, Amadeus, etc.); 
• Stakeholder management to drive product roadmap;
• Developed sales & marketing dashboard in Google Data Studio to track marketing campaign performance against online bookings; 
• Data analytics (MySQL, Hive/ Hadoop) and reporting on campaigns ROI.

As a Senior Online Marketer, I've used an agile data-driven approach and work with product owners, sales and operations to reach acquisition targets and improve the customer experience from the supply side of the marketplace:
• Product marketing (improving the customer journey and onboarding in close cooperation with PO/ product management team); 
• Product development and ownership of seller portal/ knowledge base
(from idea to a full-scale solution);
• Seller Value Proposition development;
• SEO acquisition with an emphasis on multiple landing pages
approaches (1280 landing pages, 80 product categories, 16 languages)
• Programmatic campaigns (Goole Ads, Linkedin, etc.);
• Manage agile cross-functional team to drive endless A/B experiments;
• Partner education and content marketing for better onboarding of new suppliers/ sellers. 
• Market and User research;
• Ownerships and reporting on my key metric - number of new sellers
on the platform;
• Data analysis (Google Analytics, Hotjar, R programming).

Catawiki is a Europe's fastest growing online auction house and e-commerce platform. Deloitte 2015 Technology Fast500 award winner.

As a Global Product Marketing Manager, I was responsible for new product development and Go-To-Market strategy of Digital Asset Management SaaS partner solution: https://traveltrade.visitsweden.com.

• New product development (from MVP to product/ market fit, launched Digital Asset Management (DAM) SaaS platform and scaled globally) - over 700 partners, 7 languages;
• Go-to-market strategy (including rolling out GTM plan and product improvement for regional market fit). E.g. launching a stand-alone solution to win the APAC market;
• Value proposition development;
• Market and User research;
• Content management and localisation (700+ products, 7 languages);
• Launching integrated marketing campaigns (digital, social media, PR and trade marketing).
• Partner marketing and relationship management: building relationships and forming international partnerships with existing and new clients (DMO/ destinations, airlines, cruise companies, travel operators/ travel agents, etc.).

VisitSweden is a communication company promoting Sweden, both as a brand and as a destination.
